Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Delirious Forsaken', 3: "...All infected! We're done for... Infected!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'What are they talking about? Infected... is it the Punishing Virus?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Help me keep them down! The guards are going to...', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Forsaken', 3: 'Sir! We came immediately when we saw your flare...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: "There's no time to explain... Get our guys out of here!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "We're not going to get any useful information out of them like this.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "Let them go home. I'll help the Purifying Force take out the guards with the rest of the Forsaken.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "If they remember anything while they're leaving, I swear on the Forsaken's honor, we won't hide it from the Purifying Force.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "Let's hope so. You know how the Purifying Force works.", 4: '1'}
